	<h2>The affordable, Torah-observant community in a beautiful, suburban setting&#8230;</h2>
<p>The West End of Malden is perfect for families looking to be a part of the Greater Boston Community, while being close to Downtown Boston. Our community offers Jewish day school tuition subsidies to help pay for your children&#8217;s education, home loan assistance if you are looking to purchase a house; van transportation to yeshiva day schools, an eruv, daily minyanim and full service Beit Midrash. </p>
<p>Please take a look at the Faces of our Community.</p>
